Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星总是充满了魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.55,0:00:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手常常也是演员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.45,0:00:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关重重的大屋中 侦探团展开了大冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标瞄准宝藏 LET'S GO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.25,0:00:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.65,0:02:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉就像大山啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再偷懒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.25,0:02:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来认真拾柴啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没偷懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.35,0:02:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在认真拾啊 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.05,0:02:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么点 根本不够嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.85,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 为什么柯南他却不来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.15,0:02:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又问了 刚才不是说过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.15,0:02:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.95,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一 那是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 是歌曲“七个孩子”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.25,0:03:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是“七个孩子”吧 这我知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.05,0:03:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“乌鸦啊 为什么歌唱” 是这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.95,0:03:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在放学的路上常常都唱这首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们音乐课的作业吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.15,0:03:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 是我上次说的0858
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手机上按出来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这首歌的开头一段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.05,0:03:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0858 乌鸦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.15,0:03:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时给老大发邮件的那张侧脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.05,0:03:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有种莫名的有点寂寞又有点怀念的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是因为表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.45,0:04:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是因为邮件地址的按键音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.25,0:04:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非那些家伙的老大的邮件地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是“七个孩子”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要用儿歌来作邮件地址呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那些家伙用音乐来记忆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.95,0:04:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用音乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.55,0:04:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不必在手机里存电子邮件地址了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就安全多了不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然“乌鸦啊”的节奏听起来是很像0858
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.25,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但“为什么歌唱”却无法继续下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这并不太准确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.55,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但闭上眼睛想一下几个按键音的细微差异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.75,0:04:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再组合起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.05,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就变成这个样子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.45,0:05:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个黑衣组织老大的邮件地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是不会错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.45,0:05:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是要往那里发送邮件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.45,0:05:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会做出这种暴露自己身份的事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.85,0:05:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我都慌了神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要发送邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也要在向高木警官说明情况之后啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.45,0:05:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被干掉的 高木警官的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.95,0:05:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住那个人 他是办不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们的枪口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会转到提供这个邮件地址的工藤你身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不只向高木警官通报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是对警方原原本本地说明情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起他们注意的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在事件发生后不久的话还行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在已被当作寻常绑架而结案了的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了老好人高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再有人相信这种事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 要出动警察的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须查明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个电子邮件地址的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.95,0:06:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会出现一个难以置信的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.55,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 莫非你早已经知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙的老大的电子邮件地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那家伙 到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.75,0:06:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老大的电子邮件地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不能行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.15,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 死心吧 把它忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.05,0:06:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个电子邮件地址 是决不可以打开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是潘多拉的魔盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.15,0:07:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇妙房屋的大冒险（封印篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么潘多拉的魔盒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 快告诉我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大宝藏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是里面有熊猫先生呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是天神把所有的罪恶与灾难收集到盒子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给了一个叫潘多拉的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并告诉她绝对不可以打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希腊神话故事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.75,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过越说不能打开 就会越想打开来看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太你真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.95,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 潘多拉也违背天神的嘱咐打开了盒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.15,0:07:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶与灾难就降临到了世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.75,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们为什么会在说那个潘多拉的魔盒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.15,0:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起盒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.65,0:08:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才去拾柴的时候也发现了一个奇怪的石箱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.35,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是块有个圆洞而且很古旧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像箱子一样的石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.75,0:08:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞里面密密麻麻地刻满了文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写着“仁王之石”什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很难的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难读是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.75,0:08:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能带我到你们发现那个石箱的地方去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.05,0:08:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.54,0:08:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边 石头箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点 石头箱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边在这边 就在这边哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着跑这么快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.85,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你们几个拾柴到底拾到哪里去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.15,0:09:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方居然会有间大屋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看的话 还真够破旧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.85,0:09:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是间被荒废了的大屋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉心里有点发毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.85,0:09:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.04,0:09:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经多年没人居住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.35,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.25,0:10:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是柯南你说想要看看的石箱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我们看到的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个石箱还沉在水底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.95,0:10:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里边还有条鲤鱼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.75,0:10:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想抓住那条鲤鱼 把石头拖上来后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就发现了里面刻着的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过却让鲤鱼给跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是石灯笼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 石灯笼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在日本的院子里常常能看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种用石头做成的路灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.05,0:11:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是中间放蜡烛的那个叫“火袋”的部分吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.75,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一说 看起来倒是很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果真是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.15,0:11:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那罩子和基台的部分也应该就在附近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.45,0:11:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在那里吗 小溪里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.95,0:11:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且看来还不止一个两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.05,0:11:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才忙着抓鲤鱼 完全没注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.35,0:11:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是有人把这间大屋前的石灯笼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部扔到小溪里了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.75,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人误认为这里本来就没有什么石灯笼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.25,0:11:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己好不容易才找到的暗号就不会被别人解读
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏也就不会被夺走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.35,0:12:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有宝藏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.95,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.25,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止如此 看来把石灯笼扔到小溪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是为了隐藏暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是为了隐藏罪行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条小溪的水温大约是20℃左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.05,0:13:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体尚未出现腐败迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是刚遇害不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从脖子上绳索的痕迹来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在被人勒死后给扔进小溪中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让尸体浮上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把石灯笼也扔进小溪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是谁干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.75,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该是为了宝藏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉井照尚 42岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.55,0:14:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 看出什么来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.65,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 从驾照上什么也看不出来 此外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裤边里好像有什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宝藏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.25,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用石头做成的勾玉 刻着个“炎”字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这就是宝藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.75,0:14:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 只是块奇形怪状的小石头而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.45,0:14:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人死了啊 不是讨论宝藏的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.15,0:14:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 你立刻去通知警察好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.75,0:14:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.35,0:15:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机没信号 我回帐篷那边去联系警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 当心点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 太阳也快下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 怎么能这样就回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.85,0:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 或许宝藏就在眼前呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.25,0:15:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.55,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 杀害这人的凶手很可能还潜伏在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个想被杀吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.45,0:15:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我们也只是知道这人的名字而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道他是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是个寻宝者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.65,0:15:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他的笔记本上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.15,0:16:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记满了散落在日本各地的财宝的资料与地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.75,0:16:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.35,0:16:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.45,0:16:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找这个宝藏的经过也详细地记录着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与得力的伙伴一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.55,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能把那个装模作样的小偷引出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装模作样的小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.65,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好几回被这个魔术师给逃脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.05,0:16:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁王之巢与日轮仅隔咫尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.55,0:16:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多位长老集中于繁华之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有仁王之石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.65,0:17:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢于触犯仁王愤怒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.15,0:17:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获取满手难以盈握的石块
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.25,0:17:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识取万古的真理 三水吉右卫门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.25,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三水吉右卫门 好像是幕府末期的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.13,0:17:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个为佐幕派提供援助的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关人偶师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 机关人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.45,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓机关人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是会送茶过来的那个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止如此哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.13,0:17:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把喝完的茶杯放上去后 它还会送回去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.75,0:17:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是受遥控的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.55,0:17:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 没那东西它也会自己动啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里边有什么装置呢 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.75,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说装置只有发条和齿轮 人偶还有其它很多种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.05,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有许多都流传下来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子知道得真多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.85,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为最近电视上播过啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.75,0:18:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位三水吉右卫门所制作的机关人偶栩栩如生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.85,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的诸侯和商人都很喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称机关吉右卫门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.05,0:18:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 这位机关吉右卫门所制作的仁王人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.63,0:18:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就藏在这间大屋之中吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁王人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.25,0:18:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 再怎么说也是大约140年前的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在这种破烂不堪的大屋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也早已经烂掉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 烂掉了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.95,0:19:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝藏 其实是仁王之石啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.75,0:19:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁王之巢与日轮仅隔咫尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.55,0:19:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多位长老集中于繁华之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.63,0:19:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有仁王之石 不是这么写着的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么能懂呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.85,0:19:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 那石头上刻的文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么意思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很复杂 弄不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.13,0:19:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单点说 仁王沉睡的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是最接近太阳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.95,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人们所聚集的非常热闹的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里就有仁王之石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫仁王之石的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会就是块普通的小石子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓仁王 就是金刚力士的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁王之石就是金刚石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金刚石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金刚石用英语来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.63,0:20:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是宝石之王 钻石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻 钻石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 据说钻石传入日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.13,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约就是幕府末期的时候 在时间上也很吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.05,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 那天的电视节目中说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从吉右卫门的机关人偶中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了奇怪的地图呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个寻宝者大概也是在电视画面上看到地图后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了这间大屋这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了石灯笼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.25,0:20:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 因为宝藏与同伴发生争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是这么回事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.13,0:20:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 这段文字还有下文呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 接下来才是问题的关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触犯仁王愤怒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指那些让仁王生气的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来真的存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.75,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 获取满手难以盈握的石块
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.05,0:21:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满手难以盈握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.95,0:21:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 怎么了 快告诉我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盈握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.95,0:21:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大宝石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.25,0:21:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南他似乎想不管我们自己去寻宝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.55,0:21:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.05,0:21:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.35,0:21:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 没有柯南的话就解不开暗号啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.15,0:21:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.35,0:21:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已经全解开了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.85,0:22:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.35,0:22:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与这间机关大屋还真配啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.85,0:24:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可真是很棒的作品哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.75,0:24:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您有30分钟紧张得喘不过气来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.15,0:24:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很感动 最后的时刻连眼泪都下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.05,0:24:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,务必请大家也感受一下这份感动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.65,0:24:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死人骨头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.95,0:24:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.85,0:24:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是陷阱
